---
title: Spicy Peach & Prosciutto Pizza Bianca with Ricotta, Mozzarella & Chili Flakes
description: A delicious and easy-to-make flatbread topped with sweet peaches, savory prosciutto, ricotta, mozzarella, and a touch of chili flakes for a spicy kick. Perfect for spring and summer gatherings!

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/686d3e9e5ba155634794fdc3-a971e7b8.jpeg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/686d3e9e5ba155634794fdc3-en-US.pdf
servings: 2
nutrition:
